      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Official vs Independent Platforms</h2>

      <p>The Scrabble app world splits into two camps: officially licensed apps (using the Scrabble brand) and independent word game platforms that offer similar or enhanced gameplay without the trademark.</p>

